      "value": "<p>This armor is leather armor with heavy rings sewn into it. The rings help reinforce the armor against blows from swords and axes. Ring mail is inferior to chain mail, and it's usually worn only by those who can't afford better armor.</p><p>This item is crafted from Elven Steel, renowned for its lightweight and superior craftsmanship. It reduces the weight of the item and provides a +1 bonus to Dexterity saving throws.</p><p></p>",
